#

Herb-Crusted Salmon with Asparagus and Lemon Butter Sauce

$28.99
450 kcal

Allergens:

FishDairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-ProteinLow-Carb

Tags:

SeafoodHealthyElegantDinner

Description

Deliciously baked salmon topped with fresh herbs, served alongside vibrant asparagus and a rich lemon butter sauce.

Ingredients

  • Salmon fillet: 2 pieces (6 oz each)
  • Fresh parsley: 2 tablespoons, chopped
  • Fresh dill: 2 tablespoons, chopped
  • Garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • Olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Lemon juice: 1 tablespoon
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
  • Asparagus: 1 bunch
  • Butter: 2 tablespoons
  • Lemon zest: 1 teaspoon
